// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3122 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b57dd514-0b75-562a-b308-9c198190035b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
